<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your PC ran into a problem</title>
    
    <style>
        body {
            background: #0078D7; 
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; 
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow: hidden; 
        }
        .bsod-container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 900px; 
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .bsod-smiley {
            font-size: 15vw; 
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 5vh; 
            display: block;
        }
        .bsod-main-text {
            font-size: 2.8vw; 
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 5vh;
            max-width: 80%; 
        }
        .bsod-progress {
            font-size: 1.8vw;
            margin-bottom: 7vh;
        }
        .bsod-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start; 
        }
        .bsod-qr-code {
            width: 150px; 
            height: 150px;
            margin-right: 40px;
            flex-shrink: 0; 
        }
        .bsod-details p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .bsod-details strong {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .bsod-link {
            color: #FFFFFF;
            text-decoration: underline;
            transition: background 0.2s;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .bsod-link:hover {
            background: #FFFFFF;
            color: #0078D7;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .bsod-smiley {
                font-size: 25vw;
                margin-bottom: 3vh;
            }
            .bsod-main-text {
                font-size: 4vw;
                margin-bottom: 3vh;
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            .bsod-progress {
                font-size: 2.5vw;
                margin-bottom: 5vh;
            }
            .bsod-info {
                flex-direction: column; 
            }
            .bsod-qr-code {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                margin-right: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bsod-container">
        <span class="bsod-smiley">:(</span>
        
        <p class="bsod-main-text">
            Your PC ran into a problem and needs to restart. We're just collecting some<br>
            error info, and then we'll restart for you.
        </p>

        <p class="bsod-progress">
            0% complete
        </p>
        
        <div class="bsod-info">
            <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=150x150&data=https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/troubleshoot-blue-screen-errors-5c62186c-558a-a43b-a536-193946274026" 
                 alt="QR Code" 
                 class="bsod-qr-code">
            
            <div class="bsod-details">
                <p>
                    For more information about this issue and possible fixes, visit<br>
                    <a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/troubleshoot-blue-screen-errors-5c62186c-558a-a43b-a536-193946274026" 
                       target="_blank" class="bsod-link">https://www.microsoft.com/stopcode</a>
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you call a support person, give them this info:<br>
                    Stop code: CRITICAL_PROCESS_DIED
                </p>
                <p>
                    <br>
                    <strong>Press any key to return to the last known stable state:</strong><br>
                    <a href="{{ url_for('service_list') }}" class="bsod-link">[ RETURN TO LIST ]</a>
                    <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="bsod-link">[ GO BACK ]</a>
                    <a href="{{ url_for('dashboard') }}" class="bsod-link">[ DASHBOARD ]</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>